						               													<description>Fjord Serpents is a unique and dynamic miniatures war game, set within Dark Age Scandinavia during the apex of the Viking Age.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;As a Viking Jarl you assemble your fleet and crew and compete against rivals through balanced, matched play games, or upon a heroic campaign arc of conquest and domination.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Strategic acumen, dynamic flair and a little battle luck are required to master the Viking Fjords and win. Every decision is important and every crew and ship piece plays a vital role in-game, acting independently or in unison with other pieces.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;It is fast paced Viking battle; fought as they did at the time, on the mighty Fjords which connected them, and upon the very dragon ships which gave them their greatness.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Historical in nature and deeply researched, Fjord Serpents will appeal to a wide audience of gamers; from history buffs, lovers of Viking age and culture, competitive or casual wargamers, to board game enthusiasts and strategists.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Included in the box are all the ships and crew miniatures required to field 2x Hersir size naval fleets for 2 players or enough to field one king size naval engagements for 1 player; plus all the rules, tokens, gauges, terrain and dice to play.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
